            );

            bounds: defaultBounds,
            types: ['geocode']
        };

        // Create the autocomplete object, restricting the search

        var autocomplete = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete((document.getElementById('ctl00_WebPartManager1_wp1542275338_wp384260232_LocationAutoCompleteBox_txtBoxLocation')), options);

        // When the user selects an address from the dropdown,
        // populate the address fields in the form.
        google.maps.event.addListener(autocomplete, 'place_changed', function () {
            var place = autocomplete.getPlace();

            if (!place.geometry) {
                LocationAutoCompleteclearAddress();
            } else {
                latInput.value = place.geometry.location.lat();
                lonInput.value = place.geometry.location.lng();
                placeInput.value = place.name;
                fillInAddress();
            }
        });

        function fillInAddress() {
            // Get the place details from the autocomplete object.
            var i;
            var j;
            var place = autocomplete.getPlace();

            for (i = 0; i < addressTypeMapping.length; i += 1) {
                document.getElementById(addressTypeMapping[i].id).value = '';
            }

            var distance = "";
            var radius = 5;
            // Get each component of the address from the place details
            // and fill the corresponding field on the form.
            for (i = 0; i < place.address_components.length; i++) {
                var addressType = place.address_components[i].types[0];
                if (distance == "") {
                    switch (addressType) {
                        case 'Country':
                            radius = 100
                            distance = 'Country';
                            break;
                        case 'postal_code':
                            radius = 5
                            distance = 'postal_code';
                            break;
                        case 'sublocality_level_1':
                        case 'administrative_area_level_4':
                            radius = 10
                            distance = 'administrative_area_level_4';
                            break;
                        case 'postal_town':
                            if (place.address_components[i].long_name == 'London' || place.address_components[i].long_name == 'Birmingham' || place.address_components[i].long_name == 'Manchester') {
                                distance = 'administrative_area_level_2';
                                radius = 25
                                break;
                            }
                            radius = 10
                            distance = 'sublocality_level_1';
                            break;
                        case 'administrative_area_level_3':
                            radius = 10
                            distance = 'administrative_area_level_3';
                            break;
                        case 'administrative_area_level_2':
                            radius = 25
                            distance = 'administrative_area_level_2';
                            break;
                        case 'colloquial_area':
                            if (place.address_components[i].long_name == 'Berkshire' || place.address_components[i].long_name == 'Bedfordshire' || place.address_components[i].long_name == 'Cheshire') {
                                radius = 25
                                distance = 'administrative_area_level_2';
                            }
                            break;
                        case 'administrative_area_level_1':
                            radius = 100
                            distance = 'administrative_area_level_1';
                            break;
                    }
                }
                for (j = 0; j < addressTypeMapping.length; j += 1) {
                    if (addressTypeMapping[j].type === addressType || (addressTypeMapping[j].type = 'administrative_area_level_2' && (place.address_components[i][addressTypeMapping[j].format] == 'Berkshire' || place.address_components[i][addressTypeMapping[j].format] == 'Bedfordshire' || place.address_components[i][addressTypeMapping[j].format] == 'Cheshire'))) {
                        var val = place.address_components[i][addressTypeMapping[j].format];
                        $('#' + addressTypeMapping[j].id).val(val);
                    }
                }
            }

            $(".txtdistance")[0].value = radius;
        }

        function LocationAutoCompleteclearAddress() {
            latInput.value = 0;

                    autocomplete.setBounds(new google.maps.LatLngBounds(geolocation, geolocation));
                });
            }
        }
